page.title: 02A TYPICAL DAY
page.content: I come home from school . I walk home we go into Straws the{newagents} and get a Mr freeze they are long ice pops for 5p.Then I carry on walking down home. When I go in my mum and dad are not there because they are up at the shop baking. I go in and get changed and then Claire is sometimes eating a Apple or some sweets. Then I come out of the house and we sometimes go up to the{shops}on our roller boots and we roller boot round the shops . Joanne and I go up stairs and listen to my{Duran Duran}tapes.At weekends On a Saturday I get up and go down stairs and watch{The picture show then I go in the kitchen and get some Co_ Co pops and I have a drink of coffee then I go and eat it in the room. Then I go up stairs and get dressed and then go out side.
